        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A <em>ghoul stiletto</em> is a <em>+1 dagger</em> wrapped in the still-undead skin of a ghoul. While you wield the dagger, you gain a +1 status bonus to all saves against curses and olfactory effects.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> (concentrate, divine, manipulate, olfactory)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The ghoul stiletto afflicts the next living target struck by the dagger with a terrible wound that emits the foul stench of the grave. The creature emits a stench aura in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] for 1 minute. During that time, the affected creature, as well as any creature that starts or ends its turn in the aura, must succeed at a @Check[fortitude|dc:17] save or become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (plus @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} as long as it's sickened on a critical failure). A creature that succeeds at its save is temporarily immune to all stench auras for 1 minute.</p><hr /><p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> The initial raw materials must include skin from a ghoul.</p>"
